	     <tr><td valign=top id=fs8 class=mform><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=111821><span id= >EQPyro</span></a><br><span id=notbold>159 posts<br><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Decent [3.06]</td><td valign=top class=mform width=100%><p>Not sure what you're talking about there; i have a rogue that has 5 damage bonus on her pokers and to get a 1 damage hit do happen...<br>the damage bonus he's talking about is real, does show up on weapons and it is added to your hit.<br>it works as: base damage=hit+damage bonus=total damage.&nbsp;&nbsp;not base damage+bonus=total damage<br>(10 base=20 hit+11 bonus, not 10 base+11bonus=42 hit)<br>raveena sablerose<br>41 rogue who's seen damage bonuses in action</p>&nbsp;<br><span class=sm>----------------------------</span><br><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=189481" target=_new>http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=189481</a> </td></tr>
